{"type":"answer","id":103425,"parentType":"question","parentId":13165,"uid":24007,"contents":"上面是香港摩托车驾照。下面是澳门小车驾照。都是考的。<br>\n<br>\n香港和澳门考试项目基本一样：<br>\n<br>\n摩托车：斜路8字+路考<br>\n小车：侧方停车+窄路掉头+路考<br>\n<br>\n严格说香港考试稍易，因为香港路况比澳门好一些。<br>\n这个考试都考不过的就不要上路了。上路也是马路杀手。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/k5N25DCm.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/k5N25DCm.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/k5N25DCm.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-12-13","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":1}